text: Jhang District () is a district in the Punjab province of Pakistan. The city of Jhang is the capital. ==Administration== The district of Jhang is administratively subdivided into 3 tehsils, these are: * Chiniot District (2009) * Jhang Tehsil * Shorkot Tehsil * Ahmad Pur Sial Tehsil * Athara Hazari Tehsil category:Faisalabad Division
title: Jhang District
